<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Account Suspended</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; color:
      #333; padding: 20px; } .email-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0
      auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header { text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px; } .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px;
      color: #777; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>Account Suspension Notice</h1>
      </div>
      <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
      <p>We regret to inform you that your account has been suspended as of
        {{startDate}}
        due to the following reason:</p>
      <p><strong>{{reason}}</strong></p>
      <p>If you would like more details or believe this is an error, please
        reach out to our support team to resolve the issue.</p>
      <p>We hope to assist you in resolving this matter soon.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The LAP Team</p>

      <hr />

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>